    <h1 style="color:#210400; font-weight:900;">About Foster Match</h1>
    @*<h3>@ViewBag.Message</h3>*@

    <p style="margin-left: 10vw; margin-right: 10vw;">
        The Foster Match application was created by former Family Case Manager,
        <a href="https://lgarcia223.github.io/" style="color:navy; text-decoration: underline;">Laura Garcia</a>, as an aid for foster care agencies to quickly and accurately match children in need of foster care placements
        to available foster homes.

        The goal is for agency staff, foster parents and other involved parties to be able to share up-to-date, accurate information
        regarding openings and needs to prevent unnecessary wait time for children in need of foster care placement.
    </p>

    <p style="margin-left: 10vw; margin-right: 20vw;">
